# Prices

Provides API interfaces for managing prices within <%= application_name %>

## Get All Prices

```shell
curl "<%= api_url %>/api/prices" \
  -H "Authorization: BEARER <%= api_token %>"
```

> The above command returns JSON structured like this:

```json
